    "plain_text": "Marginal Fisher Analysis: S_ij = 1 if x_i is among the k1-nearest neighbors of x_j in the same class. S_ij^P = 1 if the pair (i,j) is among the k2 shortest pairs. No Gaussian distribution assumption.",
